CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 20, 1957, pg. 16, reads: "Pastor Blesses Baby - Dr. C. A. Burrell, minister of the Mount Ararat Church, prayed for the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Robert W. Moore. They are seen here with the godparents, Mr. and Mrs. Ernest Hinton.  Dr. Burrell was not present when picture was taken. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ernest Hinton, Mrs. Hinton, Mrs. Moore, and Robert W. Moore, gathered for baptism of Moore's daughter
